M|Qual|**An|**
M|Qual|tx|1. Every element in the style spec passes the strip tst — nothing decorative remains
M|Qual|tx|2. Mood board has 3 references, each w/ a named purpose, not just a look
M|Qual|tx|3. pm passes `pm-qa` — no contradictions, forbidden elements absent, Avoid list ≥ 3 specific items
M|Qual|tx|4. 3-year tst is documented — direction is anchored to br values, not current tn
M|Qual|tx|5. qual bar has exactly 3 criteria, each specific and measurable enough for px to apply w/o asking at
M|Qual|**An|**
M|Qual|it|Mood board has > 5 references w/ no named purpose for each
M|Qual|it|Style spec contains an element that can't be justified by what it communicates
M|Qual|it|pm contains contradictory tags (candid + studio-lit, editorial + catalogue)
M|Qual|- Qu|"looks premium", "feels right", "on-br"
M|Qual|it|Direction is built from what's trending rather than what the br stands for
