M|Novi|- Ae|editorial minimalism — think magazine spread, not catalogue
M|Novi|- Li|natural, soft, directional — never harsh flash
M|Novi|- Ba|clean, neutral, textured walls — never busy
M|Novi|- Co|align to br palette; allow warm neutrals
M|Novi|- Mo|confident, authentic — not posed or commercial
M|Novi|- Wh|busy patterns, stock-photo energy, promotional overlays
M|Hour|- Ae|clean, modern, tech-forward — not clinical
M|Hour|- Vi|app UI mockups, data visualisations, clean people-w/-devices
M|Hour|- Co|br palette + white space — never dark backgrounds unless br-specified
M|Hour|- Wh|stock imagery of money, coins, piggy banks — clichéd fintech visuals
